BT /F2 17 Tf 42 806 Td (QAOA RQP Key Management Cheat Sheet v2) Tj ET
BT /F1 8 Tf 42 771 Td (Updated for Version 7.0.16.) Tj ET
BT /F1 8 Tf 42 753 Td (This sheet covers Firestore key management, usage logs, authenticated run locks,) Tj ET
BT /F1 8 Tf 42 742 Td (and the anonymous public-demo concurrency gate.) Tj ET
BT /F2 11 Tf 42 719 Td (1. Admin Environment) Tj ET
BT /F1 8 Tf 42 697 Td (Run admin commands from the repository root:) Tj ET
BT /F3 7 Tf 42 672 Td (cd "/Users/danielhug/code/qubit-lab/QAOA-Optimizer") Tj ET
BT /F1 8 Tf 42 649 Td (For Firestore admin actions, use the same secret that the Cloud Run service uses:) Tj ET
BT /F3 7 Tf 42 624 Td (export KEY_HASH_SECRET="replace-with-production-secret") Tj ET
BT /F3 7 Tf 42 615 Td (export QAOA_FIRESTORE_PROJECT_ID="your-gcp-project-id"   # optional if ADC already knows) Tj ET
BT /F3 7 Tf 42 606 Td ( it) Tj ET
BT /F1 8 Tf 42 583 Td (Default Firestore collections:) Tj ET
BT /F3 7 Tf 42 558 Td (qaoa_keys) Tj ET
BT /F3 7 Tf 42 549 Td (qaoa_usage_events) Tj ET
BT /F3 7 Tf 42 540 Td (qaoa_public_run_state) Tj ET
BT /F3 7 Tf 42 531 Td (qaoa_public_run_locks) Tj ET
BT /F1 8 Tf 42 508 Td (Production Cloud Run should use:) Tj ET
BT /F3 7 Tf 42 483 Td (QAOA_RQP_LOCAL_DEV=0) Tj ET
BT /F3 7 Tf 42 474 Td (QAOA_KEY_STORE=firestore) Tj ET
BT /F3 7 Tf 42 465 Td (QAOA_LEDGER_STORE=firestore) Tj ET
BT /F3 7 Tf 42 456 Td (KEY_HASH_SECRET=...) Tj ET
BT /F1 8 Tf 42 433 Td (Do not use `QAOA_RQP_LOCAL_DEV=1` for external demos.) Tj ET
BT /F2 11 Tf 42 410 Td (2. Create A Firestore API Key) Tj ET
BT /F1 8 Tf 42 388 Td (Create a key record. The raw API key is generated and printed exactly once.) Tj ET
BT /F1 8 Tf 42 377 Td (Only the HMAC-SHA256 hash is stored in Firestore.) Tj ET
BT /F3 7 Tf 42 352 Td (.venv/bin/python "Version 7/scripts/key_admin_firestore.py" create \\) Tj ET
BT /F3 7 Tf 42 343 Td (  --key-id customer-demo-001 \\) Tj ET
BT /F3 7 Tf 42 334 Td (  --name "Customer Name" \\) Tj ET
