BT /F1 8 Tf 42 515 Td (Authenticated `/run-qaoa` requests use a per-key run lock. Different keys can) Tj ET
BT /F1 8 Tf 42 504 Td (run in parallel. A second simultaneous run for the same key is rejected with:) Tj ET
BT /F3 7 Tf 42 479 Td (active_run_exists) Tj ET
