BT /F3 7 Tf 42 395 Td (active_run_user_agent) Tj ET
BT /F3 7 Tf 42 386 Td (active_run_ip) Tj ET
BT /F1 8 Tf 42 363 Td (Missing fields are safe:) Tj ET
BT /F3 7 Tf 42 338 Td (max_parallel_runs -> 1) Tj ET
BT /F3 7 Tf 42 329 Td (active_run_id -> none) Tj ET
BT /F3 7 Tf 42 320 Td (active_run_started_at -> none) Tj ET
BT /F3 7 Tf 42 311 Td (active_run_status -> idle) Tj ET
BT /F1 8 Tf 42 288 Td (Manual recovery command for a stuck key lock:) Tj ET
BT /F3 7 Tf 42 263 Td (.venv/bin/python "Version 7/scripts/key_admin_firestore.py" clear-lock \\) Tj ET
