BT /F3 7 Tf 42 245 Td (  --confirm) Tj ET
BT /F1 8 Tf 42 222 Td (Without `--confirm`, the command prints a warning and does not modify Firestore.) Tj ET
BT /F2 11 Tf 42 199 Td (5. Public Demo Access Without A Key) Tj ET
BT /F1 8 Tf 42 177 Td (Anonymous users still do not need an API key. They map to `public_demo`.) Tj ET
BT /F1 8 Tf 42 159 Td (`public_demo` is intentionally small:) Tj ET
BT /F3 7 Tf 42 134 Td (max_qubits: 8) Tj ET
BT /F3 7 Tf 42 125 Td (qaoa_limited max_layers: 1) Tj ET
BT /F3 7 Tf 42 116 Td (qaoa_limited max_iterations: 10) Tj ET
BT /F3 7 Tf 42 107 Td (qaoa_limited max_restarts: 1) Tj ET
BT /F3 7 Tf 42 98 Td (max_estimated_runtime_sec: 60) Tj ET
BT /F3 7 Tf 42 89 Td (max_parallel_runs: 5) Tj ET
BT /F1 7 Tf 42 24 Td (QAOA RQP Key Management Cheat Sheet v2 - Version 7.0.16) Tj ET
BT /F1 7 Tf 520 24 Td (Page 2/6) Tj ET
